{"tid":503510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警司協會發聲明 力撐朱sir繼續申訴","createTime":"2017-12-19T02:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T09:15:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b36c54d4661c952bd3893fed549e102335927af0","tid":503510,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171219/large/1513616784_e50f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F1513616784_e50f.jpg&h=680aedfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯因3年前揮警棍毆打途人，昨日被判襲擊致造成身體傷害罪名成立，警司協會就判決發出聲明，指尊重法庭裁決，但對結果感到失望，包括拒絕讓朱保釋，又表明支持朱循法律途徑繼續申訴。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，朱經緯在服務警隊期間熱愛工作，深得同僚愛戴，又表示協會一直關注今次案件，亦一直與朱保持聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57599480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57599480&d=yxQoWzmCNdQRN7MG33MByxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8ca5f364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57599480&h=937abbdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171219/57599480</a>"},{"pid":"2054f1d0280d26cd6c6f840fb49f3eb6401a7bb0","tid":503510,"uid":45684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"班同僚包唔包括華安?"},{"pid":"6932c8892e9dd0ebb7884d2466a824b9534ff8c0","tid":503510,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"封信最尾果句真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f18bf8c7788c6814b642593d5b35eb49f7b99a","tid":503510,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img sr